*
* CODING EXAMPLE 4.15.1
*
*
	 STIMER TASK,EXITRTN,DINTVL=TIMEINTV
	 ...
	 TTIMER ,MIC,TIMELEFT
	 LA    R8,0		   CLEAR R8 FOR MR INSTR
	 L     R9,TIMELEFT	   EXTRACT HI-ORDER 4 BYTES
	 L     R10,ONEMEG	   LD R10 WITH 1024 X 1024 FOR DR INSTR
	 MR    R8,R10		   HI-ORDER 4 BYTES VALUE X 1024 X 1024
	 L     R10,ONEMIL	   LD R10 WITH 1 MILLION FOR DR INSTR
	 DR    R8,R10		   DIV BY 1 MILLION TO GET SECONDS
	 CVD   R9,PKSECS	   CONV BIN SECS INTO PACK SECS
	 ...
TIMELEFT DS    D
ONEMEG   DC    X'00100000'         1024 X 1024
ONEMIL	 DC    A(1000000)	   1,000,000
PKSECS	 DS    D
